    <description>A comprehensive .NET MAUI SDK for collecting, storing, and uploading mobile sensor data. Supports 20+ sensors including accelerometer, gyroscope, GPS, battery, microphone, NFC, UWB, and more.</description>
    <tags>maui sensors accelerometer gps gyroscope magnetometer barometer nfc uwb telemetry iot mobile</tags>
